for the fonts 
Key Font Properties

font-family → sets the font of the text

font-size → sets the size of the text

font-weight → sets the thickness (boldness)

font-style → normal, italic, or oblique

font-variant → small-caps styling

font → shorthand property to set multiple font properties in one line

-->
